  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You inhale and take a charging stance, manifesting ripples of fire release chakra throughout your entire body. You perform a powerful strike with your knee meant to send opponents flying. Make a melee taijutsu attack against the creature dealing unarmed damage + 4d10 bludgeoning damage and knocking them back 15 feet on a hit.</p><p>If this jutsu is used as a <em><strong>Finisher,</strong></em> you instead make a melee taijutsu attack against the target, dealing your unarmed damage + 6d12 and knocking them back 60 feet on a hit. This attack has a +1 bonus to its critical threat range.</p>",
